{"tid":1249881,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"麻煩抗爭嘅時候冷一冷靜，收埋心中嗰頭猛獸","createTime":"2019-06-22T00:25:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-22T02:53:47.000Z","uid":34676,"like":73,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"afe9ae97e81900d8bc03b9b95dd87042341e7861","tid":1249881,"uid":34676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T00:25:27.000Z","msg":"雖然尋日大家都拎警察挑釁示威者嗰張gif 笑咗成日<br />\n<br />\n但係我發現威者入面，有啲人個情緒其實都差冇幾<br />\n<br />\n我知道大家都對警察好不滿<br />\n<br />\n前排手足有啲甚至個鼻噴哂煙<br />\n<br />\n好似見到紅布嘅西班牙鬥牛咁樣<br />\n<br />\n恨不得一個揭竿起義，攻入警總立地稱王<br />\n<br />\n但係你要知道，一衝警總就真係全部陷家產<br />\n<br />\n唔係你一個人嘅事<br />\n<br />\n人哋拉住你唔想你衝，唔係想阻你<br />\n<br />\n係因為深知勇武撚太過珍貴，少一個就少一個<br />\n<br />\n所以先更加要諗清楚，該衝嘅時候先衝<br />\n<br />\n而唔係立亂送頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n希望大家出嚟嘅時候，唔好下下諗住點樣向班狗報復<br />\n<br />\n唔好下下隻眼紅哂，俾仇恨蒙蔽<br />\n<br />\n要做到 安忍不動如大地，靜慮深密如秘藏<br />\n<br />\n用自己嘅智慧去撚狗，而唔係生命"},{"pid":"ab89058f08b9a9312ae27a283343ffc9c1fe618b","tid":1249881,"uid":34676,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T00:33:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b36a23b24e5695a295330cc7309464fdb0e220c2","tid":1249881,"uid":258047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T00:36:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"87d85f3480d392e23cfc4334551d135cc83ba3fa","tid":1249881,"uid":34676,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T00:37:29.000Z","msg":"垃圾香港人，警察都好撚過你地。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1249461\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1249461</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n見到呢個post 個樓主，完全就係我以上講嘅人辦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔想搞分化，但拜託真係要用腦"},{"pid":"fd4a78e5b1e99402507f0559a803714853475bc3","tid":1249881,"uid":65556,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T00:41:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>人哋拉住你唔想你衝，唔係想阻你<br />\n<br />\n係因為深知勇武撚太過珍貴，少一個就少一個</blockquote><br />\n呢句好同意 試問每日不斷消磨意志 又會繼續有幾多勇武<br />\n所以拜託各位 冷靜落黎諗清楚先行動 唔好犧牲"},{"pid":"db2b2878ad13ba95b33c6175c4374d9397fe6339","tid":1249881,"uid":34676,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"fd4a78e5b1e99402507f0559a803714853475bc3","tid":1249881,"uid":65556,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T00:41:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>人哋拉住你唔想你衝，唔係想阻你<br />\n<br />\n係因為深知勇武撚太過珍貴，少一個就少一個</blockquote><br />\n呢句好同意 試問每日不斷消磨意志 又會繼續有幾多勇武<br />\n所以拜託各位 冷靜落黎諗清楚先行動 唔好犧牲"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T00:44:29.000Z","msg":"係，有時要諗下人哋拉住你，係為咗救你<br />\n定係唔想你一個累全家，定還是真係鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔好下下自己發洩唔到心中果到怨氣<br />\n就屌鳩身邊拉住自己嘅人係鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />話返我地阻住哂<br />\n<br />\n其實我地喺隔離，個心都唔會好受<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d6b2546fc4cae6a0c020d4c9dded3d37b7fdcbc","tid":1249881,"uid":34676,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T00:46:36.000Z","msg":"大家出到嚟有好多都係成年人<br />\n希望真係冷靜啲審時度勢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n要衝嘅時候當然要衝，唔應該衝嘅時候就點都唔好送頭<br />\n唔好好似班畜牲咁食咗火屎，見人就想發洩<br />\n<br />\n咁做其實同班冇智商嘅黑警冇分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5fd5244b853776b067da2faf2f267f486931d79","tid":1249881,"uid":159913,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T00:51:09.000Z","msg":"地方的連登仔需要減壓<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://data.whicdn.com/images/298844185/large.jpg?t=1507433077\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdata.whicdn.com%2Fimages%2F298844185%2Flarge.jpg%3Ft%3D1507433077&h=4e221fac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://imgflip.com/s/meme/Cute-Cat.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgflip.com%2Fs%2Fmeme%2FCute-Cat.jpg&h=959a9c71&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://memestatic.fjcdn.com/pictures/Cute+cat_a8ed4d_6476355.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=htt